      "description": "Direct numerical comparison of FEA-predicted stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement against experimental measurements from N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested at two independent laboratories. All QoI percent differences within 10% acceptance bound; all E/uval ratios below 1.96.",
