      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Model form assumptions documented and justified relative to the physics of the COU; sensitivity analysis performed for key assumptions.",
      "rationale": "Implicit quasi-static FEA with large-deformation kinematics selected. Titanium alloy modeled as isotropic elastic-perfectly plastic (bilinear) based on tensile coupon data. UHMWPE block modeled as linear elastic for the F1717 loading regime. Contact interfaces modeled with augmented Lagrangian formulation. Sensitivity analysis confirms QoI insensitivity to ±10% variation in UHMWPE modulus."
