      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single ASTM F1717 compression-bending configuration (35 mm offset). The required level 3 calls for evaluation across multiple test conditions (e.g., varied offset distances or load angles) to bound the model's predictive range; this was not achieved. Achieved level 2 reflects single-condition testing. This factor is below required level and is noted as a limitation in the credibility summary."
