      "rationale": "Fixture geometry, screw torque preload, rod diameter, and block material properties matched between FEA and physical test. Measured preload torque (4.0 ± 0.1 N·m) replicated in FEA via bolt pretension element. Equivalency confirmed; residual discrepancy in block modulus (±5%) assessed as contributing less than 1% to QoI difference."
